<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="page-title">自定义谜境</view>
  <view class="page-subtitle">默认已经帮你放好一张样图，可以直接生成谜境。你也可以随时换成相册里的其他照片。</view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">生成新谜境</view>
      <view class="chip">{{isUsingDefaultImage ? '默认样图' : '相册图片'}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="uploader" bindtap="handleChooseImage">
      <image wx:if="{{selectedImagePath}}" class="uploader-image" src="{{selectedImagePath}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
      <view wx:else class="uploader-empty">
        <view class="uploader-empty-title">默认样图加载中</view>
        <view class="uploader-empty-desc">如果默认图没显示，可以点下面按钮重新恢复，或者换成相册照片</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="button-grid top-actions">
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleUseDefaultImage">使用默认样图</button>
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleChooseImage">改成相册照片</button>
      <button class="primary-btn compact-btn" loading="{{generating}}" bindtap="handleCreateLevel">直接生成谜境</button>
    </view>
    <view class="field-label">谜境名称</view>
    <input class="text-input" value="{{draftTitle}}" maxlength="30" placeholder="给你的谜境起个名字" bindinput="handleTitleInput" />
    <view class="field-label">切片规格</view>
    <picker range="{{layoutOptions}}" range-key="label" value="{{layoutIndex}}" bindchange="handleLayoutChange">
      <view class="picker-field">{{layoutOptions[layoutIndex].label}} · {{layoutOptions[layoutIndex].timeLimit}} 秒 · {{layoutOptions[layoutIndex].hints}} 次提示</view>
    </picker>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view class="card-title">导入好友谜境码</view>
      <view class="chip">复制粘贴</view>
    </view>
    <view class="card-desc">朋友把谜境码发给你后，直接粘贴在这里就能恢复同一张谜境图。</view>
    <textarea class="code-input" maxlength="-1" value="{{importCode}}" placeholder="把朋友发来的谜境码粘贴到这里" bindinput="handleImportInput"></textarea>
    <view class="grid-two">
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handlePasteCode">粘贴谜境码</button>
      <button class="secondary-btn" bindtap="handleImportCode">导入并保存</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">我的谜境</view>
  <view wx:if="{{customLevels.length === 0}}" class="empty-tip">还没有自定义谜境。现在直接点“直接生成谜境”就会使用默认样图创建第一关。</view>

  <block wx:for="{{customLevels}}" wx:key="levelId">
    <view class="card custom-level-card">
      <view class="row">
        <image class="thumb" src="{{item.customMeta.imagePath}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        <view class="custom-level-main">
          <view class="card-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="card-desc">{{item.chapterTitle}} · {{item.rows}}x{{item.cols}} · {{item.timeLimit}} 秒</view>
          <view class="custom-meta">
            {{item.completed ? ('已揭晓 · 谜境评级 ' + item.stars + ' · 最少步数 ' + item.bestMoves) : '未揭晓'}}
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="button-grid">
        <button class="secondary-btn" data-level-id="{{item.levelId}}" bindtap="handlePlay">进入谜境</button>
        <button class="secondary-btn" data-level-id="{{item.levelId}}" bindtap="handleCopyCode">复制谜境码</button>
        <button class="secondary-btn danger-btn" data-level-id="{{item.levelId}}" bindtap="handleDelete">删除</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>

  <canvas canvas-id="processorCanvas" class="offscreen-canvas"></canvas>
</view>
